<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA082890-0015 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 267883 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 28, 1990, Tuesday, Ventura County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 1 
