<HEADLINE>
<P>
3 YOUNG WOMEN SLAIN NEAR UNIVERSITY OF FLORIDA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
GAINESVILLE, Fla. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A young college student was found slain in her apartment early Monday, hours 
after police found two other young women dead in another apartment near the 
University of Florida, authorities said. The three slayings on the eve of the 
fall term led parents to flood the university community with worried calls. 
</P>
</TEXT>
