<P>
By ROSE APODACA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Commissioner Betty Wiley was unanimously approved by the Planning Commission as 
its representative to serve on the Citizens Advisory Committee, which will help 
to revise the city's General Plan. 
</P>
<P>
