Janet Cater, right, at party for Orange County Mothers Against Drunk Driving. 
Below, other MADD supporters: State Sen. Edward R. Royce, left, Assemblyman 
Curt Pringle and Janine DuMontelle. JOHN FUNG / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
